snippet.title: The Burst - Official Release Date Trailer | Upload VR Showcase
snippet.description: The Burst is a VR parkour shooter developed by GoRapid Studio. Players will fight, climb, and leap against a tyrannical warband to bring order to a prison planet once and for all. The Burst is launching on August 8 for Meta Quest and Steam VR.
